\nvaluable resource to implement \\textit{some} coherent unitary channel. We\nillustrate our findings for the case of single-qubit unitary channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 May 2018 16:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2018 09:23:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2018 11:43:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-22"}
