i-analytic models of galaxy formation. In terms of halo\ngrowth, we find a late-assembling halo fraction within a factor-of-two of our\nlate bloomer fraction. However, sufficiently delaying star formation in such\nhalos may be a challenge for the baryon component of such models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 May 2018 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Nov 2018 19:37:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-26"}
