 method achieves superior performance over the\ncompeting baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 May 2018 09:24:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 08:03:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
