 importance of properly resolving the (a)SI at high dust-to-gas\nratios and planetesimal collapse simulations, leading else wise to potentially\nincomplete results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 May 2018 11:23:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-18"}
