h nonlocal viscosity converges strongly as the filter parameter\n$\\alpha\\rightarrow~0$ to a solution of the equations (INSF).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 May 2018 11:27:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-15"}
